[i](Gain the next level as a sorcery to add its ability.)[/i]
Whenever you put one or more counters on a permanent you control for the first time each turn, draw a card.
[b]Level 2[/b] {1}{W}
Whenever you attack, put a +1/+1 counter on up to one target creature.
[b]Level 3[/b] {3}{W}
Whenever you attack with three or more creatures, double the amount of counters on any number of target permanents you control.
